{
  "stem": "26609.15",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And on that yellow square was a big and black P, a P-- Pole for Pole.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because there were others, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were others from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They all were grouped there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So, a P is a Pole.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Then they marched us in in a queue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We had to face into that in a huge [? hole. ?] And there were among us about-- they segregated groups.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 30-- 25, 30.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we had to stood and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] strange.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "As sad I was that I left my child and I knew nothing about my family, I still thought-- I don't know how it came-- I still had a bit of humor in myself.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I thought we stand here like horses one after the other, a queue.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they would soon come and look into our teeth like horses on a market.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "People on the opposite us stood all the Germans-- men and women, wealthy people from farms, mostly farms.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they came up one by one and looked at each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I thought, yes, like horses on the market to sell.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They looked at us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That person who gave us that P left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He was with the transport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "With us he came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But the people-- the Germans from opposite-- mostly they were well dressed and well fed from German-- mostly farms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But they were not peasants.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They were well dressed and well behaving people that had farms, but they had workers on the farms.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They didn't work themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They came up and looked at each other-- on the face, on the hands.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
